 have pulled themselves up by their bootstraps. So what do you say to that poor kid with the teenage mom whose dad isn\u2019t in his life? Give up, there is nothing you can do. Really? Do you believe that? Here is an odd thought. Instead of coming up with an answer maybe listen to what he has to say. Specifically what one such kid has to say to his own son."), mdx("h2", null, "Greatness Is Upon You"), mdx("p", null, "This is one of my favorite people on the planet, Eric Thomas. When I\u2019m down he is my best kept secret. I\u2019ve watched this video countless times."), mdx("p", null, mdx("a", {
